---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../consts";
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`HVAC Installation Tupelo, MS | ${SITE.name}`}
  description="HVAC installation guidance for Tupelo, MS homes: sizing considerations, replacement timing, and quote request steps."
  canonical={`${SITE.url}/hvac-installation-tupelo/`}
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container surface service">
      <p class="eyebrow">HVAC Installation Tupelo</p>
      <h1>HVAC Installation and Replacement in Tupelo, MS</h1>
      <p>
        If your current system is older, inconsistent, or costly to maintain, new HVAC installation may be the right
        next step. In Tupelo, sizing for humidity, insulation conditions, and duct performance is just as important as
        choosing equipment brand.
      </p>
      <h2>What affects replacement decisions</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Frequent repairs across recent seasons.</li>
        <li>Uneven temperatures and comfort complaints.</li>
        <li>Noise, poor airflow, and humidity control issues.</li>
        <li>System age and efficiency target for the home.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Request a quote with home details and ZIP code. If you only need tune-ups, see
        <a href="/hvac-maintenance-tupelo/"> HVAC maintenance</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="button primary" href="/#request-service">Request Service</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">Get a Quote</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/tupelo-hvac-guide/">Read the Tupelo HVAC Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .service {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
